          "question": "What if my loved one lives in a county that's not served?",
          "answer": "SCSEP is not available statewide. If your loved one's county isn't served by Greater Memphis Workforce, NWTHRA, or ETHRA, they cannot participate in this program. Contact (731) 989-5111 to confirm county coverage or ask about other employment programs."
